headline: ComEd Announces $130,000 in Scholarships to City Colleges Line Worker Training Program
summary: CHICAGO, July 23, 2025--Today, ComEd joined the City Colleges of Chicago (CCC) and community leaders to celebrate the latest class of graduates of the Dawson Technical Institute (DTI) Overhead Electrical Line Worker (OELW) program and to announce an investment of up to $130,000 in scholarships available for the program.
